#lem: anše[equid]; Šakkan[1]DN; kaš[run]; ki[place]; aŋ[measure]

19. dub-sar gal-zu {d}nisaba-kam-me-en
#lem: dubsar[scribe]; galanzu[wise]; Nisabak[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=19

